Module210000Name = LemonFacturX
Module210000Desc = Automatic Factur-X EN16931 e-invoice generation

LemonFacturXSetup = LemonFacturX setup
LemonFacturXEnabled = Enable Factur-X conversion
LemonFacturXBankAccount = Bank account (IBAN/BIC)
LemonFacturXPaymentMeans = Default payment means
LemonFacturXPaymentMeansHint = UNTDID 4461 code. 30/58 (credit transfer) require an IBAN: without a configured bank account, the payment means block is omitted from the XML (BR-61). 59 (SEPA direct debit) publishes the creditor ICS (Dolibarr constant PRELEVEMENT_ICS), the mandate reference and the IBAN of the third party's default bank account.
PaymentMeans30 = Credit transfer
PaymentMeans58 = SEPA credit transfer
PaymentMeans59 = SEPA direct debit
PaymentMeans49 = Direct debit (national)
LemonFacturXEndpointScheme = Electronic address scheme (endpoint BT-34/BT-49)
LemonFacturXEndpointSchemeHint = Scheme code of the routing electronic address (URIID). 0225 = SIREN in the French PPF directory (Plateformes Agréées network, default for the French reform). 0002/0009 = SIREN/SIRET ISO 6523 if your platform requires it. For a third party without SIREN (foreign), the email is used automatically.
EndpointScheme0225 = SIREN (PPF directory, French reform)
EndpointScheme0002 = SIREN (ISO 6523)
EndpointScheme0009 = SIRET (ISO 6523)
LemonFacturXLegalIdScheme = Legal identifier (BT-30 / BT-47)
LemonFacturXLegalIdSchemeHint = Identifier carried by SpecifiedLegalOrganization. ISO 6523: 0002 = SIREN (9 digits), 0009 = SIRET (14 digits). The default "SIRET (0009)" is ISO 6523 compliant and accepted by Chorus Pro. "SIRET (0002)" reproduces the 2.1.x behaviour.
LegalIdSchemeSiret0009 = SIRET, schemeID 0009 (default, ISO 6523 compliant)
LegalIdSchemeSiren0002 = SIREN, schemeID 0002 (ISO 6523 compliant, rejected by Chorus Pro)
LegalIdSchemeSiret0002 = SIRET, schemeID 0002 (2.1.x legacy)
LemonFacturXVatDueDateType = VAT point date option (BT-8)
LemonFacturXVatDueDateTypeHint = Your company's VAT option: 72 = VAT on payments (cash accounting, French default for services), 5 = VAT on invoicing (debits, mandatory mention if opted in). Omitted from the XML if empty. Only emitted on taxed categories (S).
VatDueDateTypeNone = Not specified (omitted from XML)
VatDueDateType72 = VAT on payments (encaissements)
VatDueDateType5 = VAT on debits (débits)
LemonFacturXBt23Process = Business process (BT-23)
LemonFacturXBt23ProcessHint = BusinessProcess of the document context. Chorus Pro B2G: A1 (invoice deposit), A2 (already paid invoice)... French reform (PPF/PDP): B1, S1, S2, M1... Leave empty to omit (tolerated as long as your platform does not require it).
LemonFacturXBrCheck = EN16931 business rules check
LemonFacturXBrCheckHint = Checks a subset of the EN16931 Schematron rules before injection (BR-CO-10..17, BR-27, BR-61, BR-IC-11/12, VAT category consistency...). Violations block in strict mode, otherwise they are added to the warnings.
LemonFacturXVeraPdfPath = veraPDF binary path (optional)
LemonFacturXVeraPdfPathHint = If set, every generated PDF is validated as PDF/A-3b by veraPDF after injection (https://verapdf.org). Non blocking: a failure adds a warning. Slows down generation by a few seconds.
LemonFacturXInfo = Generated PDF invoices will automatically be converted to Factur-X EN16931 (PDF/A-3 with embedded CrossIndustryInvoice XML). IBAN and BIC are read from the selected bank account.
LemonFacturXDiagTitle = Mandatory information diagnostic
LemonFacturXDiagResults = Factur-X EN16931 + BR-FR rules check
LemonFacturXDiagSellerName = Seller company name
LemonFacturXDiagSellerAddress = Seller address
LemonFacturXDiagSellerVAT = Intra-community VAT number
LemonFacturXDiagSellerVATFranchise = not required (French VAT franchise, art. 293 B CGI) — the SIREN is published as tax identifier
LemonFacturXDiagSellerSIRET = SIRET / SIREN
LemonFacturXDiagSellerEmail = Seller email
LemonFacturXDiagIBAN = Bank account IBAN
LemonFacturXDiagBIC = Bank account BIC
LemonFacturXDiagBankNotFound = Bank account not found
LemonFacturXDiagBankNotSet = No bank account selected
LemonFacturXDiagModuleBankEnabled = Bank module enabled
LemonFacturXDiagModuleBankDisabled = Bank module disabled (required to manage the bank account)
LemonFacturXDiagModuleInvoiceEnabled = Invoice module enabled
LemonFacturXDiagModuleInvoiceDisabled = Invoice module disabled (required to generate invoices)
LemonFacturXDiagForceFontOk = Embedded PDF font forced (MAIN_PDF_FORCE_FONT)
LemonFacturXDiagForceFontMissing = MAIN_PDF_FORCE_FONT not set — set it to "pdfahelvetica" (Setup > Other), otherwise the PDF is not PDF/A-3 compliant (fonts not embedded)
LemonFacturXDiagExecEnabled = exec() function available (injection subprocess)
LemonFacturXDiagExecDisabled = exec() function disabled on this server — Factur-X injection is impossible (disable_functions in php.ini)
LemonFacturXDiagPhpCliOk = PHP CLI binary
LemonFacturXDiagPhpCliNotFound = The configured PHP CLI binary cannot be found or is not executable: %s
LemonFacturXDiagMulticurrencyNote = Multicurrency module enabled: invoices in a foreign currency are NOT converted to Factur-X (documented limitation, the classic PDF is kept)
LemonFacturXDiagFixLink = Fix
LemonFacturXDiagAllOk = All mandatory information is filled in!

LemonFacturXStrictMode = Error handling mode
LemonFacturXStrictModeHint = Best-effort: if Factur-X generation fails, the classic PDF is delivered with a warning. Strict: blocks generation with a visible error if the XML is invalid or the PDF injection fails. Note: even in strict mode, the classic PDF already generated by Dolibarr remains on disk.
LemonFacturXStrictModeBestEffort = Best-effort (default, non blocking)
LemonFacturXStrictModeStrict = Strict (blocks if Factur-X fails)
LemonFacturXPhpCliPath = PHP CLI binary path
LemonFacturXPhpCliPathHint = Used by the PDF injection subprocess. Leave "php" if the binary is in the PATH, otherwise absolute path (e.g. /usr/bin/php8.2). Never use PHP_BINARY in FPM context.
LemonFacturXLegalNotes = Mandatory French legal mentions (BR-FR-05)
LemonFacturXNotePMD = Late payment penalties (PMD)
LemonFacturXNotePMT = Recovery indemnity (PMT)
LemonFacturXNoteAAB = Early payment discount (AAB)

LemonFacturXUpdateAvailable = New version available
LemonFacturXUpdateAvailableMsg = A newer version of the module is published on GitHub (%s, current: %s).
LemonFacturXUpdateSeeRelease = See the release and upgrade instructions

LemonFacturXBtnVerify = Verify Factur-X
LemonFacturXBtnRegenerate = Regenerate Factur-X
LemonFacturXMsgNoPdf = No PDF found for this invoice — generate the document first.
LemonFacturXMsgNoFacturX = No Factur-X XML embedded in %s — use "Regenerate Factur-X".
LemonFacturXMsgVerifyOk = %s: embedded Factur-X XML found, EN16931 XSD valid and business rules checked.
LemonFacturXMsgVerifyKo = %s: embedded Factur-X XML found but not compliant:
LemonFacturXMsgRegenerateFailed = PDF regeneration failed
LemonFacturXMsgSuccess = Factur-X EN16931 e-invoice embedded in PDF %s.
LemonFacturXMsgSuccessWithWarnings = Factur-X EN16931 e-invoice embedded in PDF %s. %s non blocking warning(s) to fix for full compliance:

LemonFacturXErrMulticurrency = invoice in a foreign currency (%s ≠ company currency %s) — unsupported: the XML would diverge from the visible PDF (documented limitation)
LemonFacturXErrLocalTax = invoice with local taxes (localtax1/2) — unsupported: EN16931 only represents VAT, the XML total would diverge from the visible PDF total (documented limitation)
LemonFacturXErrNoDate = invoice has no issue date
LemonFacturXErrNoThirdparty = buyer third party not found (fetch_thirdparty failed)
LemonFacturXErrNoMysoc = issuing company ($mysoc) not initialised
LemonFacturXErrInvalidXml = invalid XML
LemonFacturXErrBrViolations = EN16931 business rules violated
LemonFacturXErrTempDir = unable to create a temporary file in %s
LemonFacturXErrTempWrite = unable to write the temporary XML in %s
LemonFacturXErrNoExec = the exec() function is disabled on this server
LemonFacturXErrPhpCliChars = LEMONFACTURX_PHP_CLI_PATH contains forbidden characters (expected: alphanumeric path, "/ . _ - : ( ) \" and space)
LemonFacturXErrPhpCliNotFound = the configured PHP binary cannot be found or is not executable: %s
LemonFacturXErrInjectFailed = PDF injection failed
LemonFacturXHintPdfKept = classic PDF kept without Factur-X
LemonFacturXHintPdfKeptShort = classic PDF kept
LemonFacturXHintBestEffort = best-effort mode

LemonFacturXWarnSellerName = seller company name missing
LemonFacturXWarnSellerAddress = seller company address missing
LemonFacturXWarnSellerZip = seller company zip code missing
LemonFacturXWarnSellerTown = seller company town missing
LemonFacturXWarnSellerVAT = intra-community VAT number missing (company)
LemonFacturXWarnSellerSIRET = SIRET/SIREN missing (company) — mandatory BR-FR-10
LemonFacturXWarnSellerEndpoint = seller electronic address missing (no SIREN/SIRET, no email) — mandatory BR-FR-13 (BT-34)
LemonFacturXWarnSellerSIRETLen = the seller SIRET must contain exactly 14 digits (BT-30), %s entered — a 9-digit SIREN is rejected by Chorus Pro
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerName = buyer name missing
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerAddress = buyer address missing
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerZip = buyer zip code missing
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerTown = buyer town missing
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerEndpoint = buyer electronic address missing (no SIREN/SIRET, no email) — mandatory BR-FR-12 (BT-49)
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerSIRENRouting = buyer SIREN/SIRET missing — required for routing on the Plateformes Agréées network (endpoint BT-49 schemeID 0225); an email alone is not routable
LemonFacturXWarnBuyerSIRETLen = the buyer SIRET must contain exactly 14 digits (BT-47), %s entered
LemonFacturXWarnNoBank = no bank account configured in the module
LemonFacturXWarnNoForceFont = MAIN_PDF_FORCE_FONT not set — the generated PDF is not guaranteed PDF/A-3 (fonts not embedded); set "pdfahelvetica" in Setup > Other
LemonFacturXWarnPaymentMeansOmitted = payment means %s (credit transfer) omitted from XML: no IBAN configured (BR-61 — configure a bank account in the module)
LemonFacturXWarnDirectDebitNoICS = SEPA direct debit: creditor ICS missing (BT-90) — set the Dolibarr constant PRELEVEMENT_ICS
LemonFacturXWarnDirectDebitNoRUM = SEPA direct debit: mandate reference (RUM) missing (BT-89) — fill in the third party's default bank account with its mandate reference
LemonFacturXWarnCreditNoteNoSource = credit note without a linked source invoice: the reference to the original invoice (BG-3, mandatory French mention) cannot be emitted — create the credit note from the original invoice
LemonFacturXWarnAllNegativeLines = fully negative invoice that is not a credit note: lines emitted as-is, the XML violates BR-27 (use a Dolibarr credit note)
LemonFacturXWarnSituationInvoice = situation (progress billing) invoice: emitted as TypeCode 380, but the mapping of cumulative amounts/retentions is not guaranteed compliant (documented limitation)
LemonFacturXWarnRoundingAdjusted = VAT rounding gap of %s spread on the main category to guarantee BR-CO-14 (check the totals)
LemonFacturXWarnTaxMismatch = gap of %s between line VAT and the invoice VAT total, not attributable (no taxed category)
LemonFacturXWarnTaxRecomputed = VAT of category %s recomputed from its basis (%s instead of %s) to satisfy BR-CO-17 — the gap with the Dolibarr total comes from per-line rounding (check the rounding mode)
LemonFacturXWarnTotalsMismatch = XML grand total (%s) differs from the Dolibarr total (%s) — local taxes or inconsistent lines; the XML favours EN16931 internal consistency (BR-CO-15)
LemonFacturXWarnVeraPdfNotFound = veraPDF not found or not executable: %s (LEMONFACTURX_VERAPDF_PATH)
LemonFacturXWarnVeraPdfFailed = veraPDF: the generated PDF is not PDF/A-3b compliant (details in syslog) — check MAIN_PDF_FORCE_FONT and the PDF template images
LemonFacturXWarnBrPrefix = EN16931 business rule:

